  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "OBRIX through Aquatic Chain with Drift as the defining feature. Supersaw source (src1Type=6) through proc1 LP creates a rich harmonic base. Drift at maximum 6 voices with diffusion 0.72 and stereoSpread 0.85 turns the supersaw into a massive ensemble texture that no simple unison/detune approach could match — the Brownian walk gives each voice an independent, non-repetitive trajectory. Fathom Character 0.35. Tide in AutoFilter at 0.08 Hz. Reef at size 0.55. The resulting sound is OBRIX transcribed into a 6-voice string section filtered through water.",
  "tags": ["obrix", "supersaw", "aquatic-chain", "drift", "ensemble", "atmosphere", "brownian", "fx-showcase"],
